<subSubSection pageId="152" pageNumber="550" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="152.[166,1372,2624,3326]" pageId="152" pageNumber="550">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[168,522,3136,3169]" pageId="152" pageNumber="550">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Vulnerable on The IUCN Red List. The Kahuzi Mouse Shrew is known from a few specimens from a single small location, where the habitats are threatened by human activities such asillegal logging, coltan mining, and draining of swamp areas.
</paragraph>
